channel.title: Gio's Server Dev 1.0
channel.description:
Ive finnaly decided to add this here. The server is dodian source, has some bugs, and a few things needed to be added. I am bassically looking for Mods, Coders, Forum Mods, Beta Testers, forum designer, and maybe a hoster. This is my first dev team, so bare with me. If you want the link to the forum pm me. Also im only on the computer for maybe 2 hours a day. I added new training places, kept some of the old ones, added a new boss, added a new ring that i have never seen in a server before.
